title: Understanding Workbook Merging
text: When you have multiple copies of a workbook with the same file name, consider how Excel handles these files. Does it allow merging, or does it treat them as separate entities?

title: File Name Conflicts
text: Think about what happens when two files with the same name exist in the same location. How does the system handle this situation?

title: Merging Capabilities
text: Consider whether Excel has a built-in feature to merge workbooks with the same name automatically.
